@startuml 图4-2-2-管理员功能模块图
!theme plain
top to bottom direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei UI"
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #666666

title 图4-2-2 管理员功能模块图

rectangle "后台管理员功能" as ROOT #EAF3FF

rectangle "用户管理" as M1 #FFFFFF
rectangle "小说管理" as M2 #FFFFFF
rectangle "分类管理" as M3 #FFFFFF
rectangle "评论管理" as M4 #FFFFFF
rectangle "数据统计" as M5 #FFFFFF
rectangle "系统设置" as M6 #FFFFFF

ROOT -down-> M1
ROOT -down-> M2
ROOT -down-> M3
ROOT -down-> M4
ROOT -down-> M5
ROOT -down-> M6

rectangle "用户查询/状态维护/禁用处理" as M1A
rectangle "小说新增编辑/上下架/章节维护" as M2A
rectangle "文库管理/标签管理/关联维护" as M3A
rectangle "评论审核/违规删除/状态更新" as M4A
rectangle "阅读收藏鲜花统计/趋势分析" as M5A
rectangle "参数配置/推荐位配置/日志查看" as M6A

M1 -down-> M1A
M2 -down-> M2A
M3 -down-> M3A
M4 -down-> M4A
M5 -down-> M5A
M6 -down-> M6A

note bottom of ROOT
统一通过 /api/admin/** 访问，基于 JWT 角色鉴权
end note

@enduml
